print(result)


ğŸ“Œ return sends value back.

6ï¸âƒ£ Real Example

Check even or odd using function:

def check_even(num):
    if num % 2 == 0:
        return "Even"
    else:
        return "Odd"

print(check_even(10))
print(check_even(7))

